data.description: Beautiful country living just outside historic Carthage! This home boasts a large 4 bedroom / 3 bathroom home with over 2200 sqft of living space including a huge primary suite with a large, custom walk-in closet! Enjoy entertaining with this huge living space, dining space, and a nice wrap-around kitchen! Outside you'll find 2 outbuildings, including a huge workshop and a barn with a built-in greenhouse! An ample amount of fruit trees and space for growing family to enjoy this beautiful 5 acres!
